snippet.title: Johnny Depp Releases SHOCKING New Tapes | Amber Heard Dares Him to 'TELL THE WORLD'
snippet.description:
SHOCKING New Tapes show Amber Heard dares Johnny Depp to 'tell the world' he was victim of domestic abuse: 'See who believes you'. 'I have never been able to overpower you ... and there’s a jury and there’s a judge will see that there’s a very big difference between me and you,' she is heard saying. So who is right here, what is the real story and what is the deal with the Justice for Johnny Depp movements?
